  <FLAVOURTEXT>
    <LOCALISED_TEXT LanguageCode="en-US"><![CDATA[Its hunger and ire are no less for being wrought of lies and mist.]]></LOCALISED_TEXT>
    <LOCALISED_TEXT LanguageCode="it-IT"><![CDATA[Anche se plasmato da nebbia e bugie, la sua fame e la sua collera non sono certo trascurabili.]]></LOCALISED_TEXT>
    <LOCALISED_TEXT LanguageCode="de-DE"><![CDATA[Seinen Hunger und Zorn macht es nicht geringer, dass er aus Lügen und Nebel besteht.]]></LOCALISED_TEXT>
    <LOCALISED_TEXT LanguageCode="fr-FR"><![CDATA[Bien que forgées de mensonges et de brume, sa faim et sa colère sont bien réelles.]]></LOCALISED_TEXT>
    <LOCALISED_TEXT LanguageCode="es-ES"><![CDATA[Su hambre y su ira no son menores por estar hecho de mentiras y niebla.]]></LOCALISED_TEXT>
    <LOCALISED_TEXT LanguageCode="jp-JA"><![CDATA[嘘と霧から生み出されたものにも関わらず、その飢えと怒りは力を持つ。]]></LOCALISED_TEXT>
    <LOCALISED_TEXT LanguageCode="ko-KR"><![CDATA[Its hunger and ire are no less for being wrought of lies and mist.]]></LOCALISED_TEXT>
    <LOCALISED_TEXT LanguageCode="ru-RU"><![CDATA[Его голод и ярость ничуть не слабее от того, что они сделаны из обманов и тумана.]]></LOCALISED_TEXT>
    <LOCALISED_TEXT LanguageCode="pt-BR"><![CDATA[Sua fome e sua ira não são aplacadas pelo fato de ser feito de mentiras e brumas.]]></LOCALISED_TEXT>
  </FLAVOURTEXT>
